  <brief_title>Compassionate Use of Pennsaid Topical Lotion (Diclofenac) in Osteo or Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Non-blinded, Non-placebo Controlled, Compassionate Use, Open Treatment, Open-ended Program of the Safety of Pennsaid Topical Lotion (Diclofenac) in the Treatment of Osteo or Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
